00:10:52.600 --> 00:10:53.440
Qianfan.

00:10:53.840 --> 00:10:55.120
Vieux renard.

00:10:55.440 --> 00:10:57.900
J'ai peur que tu aies fait plus de mal que moi.

00:10:59.480 --> 00:11:00.840
Tu me calomnies !

00:11:03.000 --> 00:11:04.240
Laquelle de mes actions

00:11:05.680 --> 00:11:07.440
